				<td colspan="2"><span><img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-10.gif" border="0" alt="Blushing" hspace="2" />I just started a Bard and think I will enjoy playing her but I just don't understand the spells we have and what is called twisting. Are we supposed to be able to sing or play two or more songs at once? For instance, if I am using Heal and then cast Selo's, Heal stops and same for all other spells. Is that the way it should be or should I be able to use Heal and Jonthan's War Song at the same time. Someone Please sort this out for me.
<br />
I was told to use macro's and I set a couple up but not sure I did it right. I made one for Heal as follows: /stopsong, /pause 20, /cast 1. Heal is first one on my spell thing. Is this how it's supposed to be? Please Help!!</span></td>
